    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront so buyers can make a well-informed decision. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple scratches, dents, and paint fading across various panels. The interior has seen better days, with worn seating, damaged trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will likely require repairs or parts replacement \u2014 a pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic is strongly recommended. This listing is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle, someone looking for parts, or a mechanically inclined individual who can address the issues themselves. Priced accordingly to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
