    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "\u2728 Pristine & Perfect \u2014 A Rare Mint-Condition Gem! \u2728 This is the one you've been waiting for! This car is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 flawless inside and out, with everything working exactly as it should. The exterior shines like it just rolled off the showroom floor, the interior is spotless and fresh, and mechanically it's in top-notch shape. No issues, no surprises \u2014 just a beautifully maintained vehicle that's ready to impress from day one. If you want the very best, this is it! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
