    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet your next great adventure. This stunning beauty arrives with a presence that turns heads before the engine even whispers to life. Every surface gleams with the kind of care that only comes from true devotion \u2014 immaculate paint that catches the light like liquid glass, an interior that still carries that subtle richness of a well-loved but meticulously maintained cabin. She's been cherished, not just driven. The kind of car that makes your daily commute feel like a Sunday morning cruise through open countryside. Whether you're chasing horizons or simply want something that reflects your own high standards, this is a rare find that won't wait long.",
      "price": 45000.0,
